    	<section class="main-section" id="Introduction">
    		<header>All you need to know about  COVID -19 </header>
        <p> Why a lesson after quizzes ? This because life takes a test and then teaches a lesson , and so does this platform !! </p>
    		<article>
      
    		 <h4>What is COVID-19?</h4>
    		  <li>Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) is an infectious disease caused by severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).</li>
    		  <li>It was first identified in December 2019 in Wuhan, Hubei, China, and has resulted in an ongoing pandemic.</li>
    		  <li>Traces of the virus have been found in wastewater that was collected from Milan and Turin, Italy, on 18 December 2019.</li>
    		  <li>As of 29 June 2020, more than 10.1 million cases have been reported across 188 countries and territories, resulting in more than 501,000 deaths. </li>
          <div class="img-container">
          <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/Novel_Coronavirus_SARS-CoV-2.jpg/375px-Novel_Coronavirus_SARS-CoV-2.jpg" alt="Italian Trulli">
          </div>
          
      
          
          
          
